# Frontend Orchestrator

- Task JSON lives in `agent_tasks/{pending,active,completed,failed}/`
- Each repair task uses branch `agent/fix-{id}-{slug}`
- Never exceed 20 file edits or 5 retries per task
- Always run `npm run qa:frontend` before marking complete
- Prefer rule-based + LLM fixes; write Cursor brief if ambiguous
- Follow-up tasks scan adjacent directories after success
